Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Phase 1 of the iHotel modular refactoring:

NEW FILES:
- server/adapters/platform-adapter.js  — Abstract PlatformAdapter base class + AdapterPool
- server/adapters/tb-adapter.js        — ThingsBoard concrete adapter (full capability)
- server/adapters/index.js             — Factory registry for adapter selection
- server/services/sse.service.js       — SSE broadcast + batching layer (extracted from index.js)
- server/services/state.service.js     — Per-hotel in-memory state management (extracted from index.js)

PlatformAdapter interface defines:
  authenticate(), listDevices(), getDeviceState(), getAllDeviceStates(),
  getDeviceAttributes(), sendTelemetry(), sendAttributes(), subscribe(),
  verifyCommand(), getCapabilities(), getWsToken(), getWsUrl()

Next: PR2 will extract control/room/scene services and rewire index.js.
