NEW FILES:
- server/services/audit.service.js    — addLog() with DB write + SSE batch
- server/services/control.service.js  — sendControl(), controlToTelemetry(), relay mapping,
                                         vacateRoom(), restoreOccupied(), NOT_OCCUPIED timers,
                                         coerceTelemetry(), activity detection
- server/services/room.service.js     — fetchAndBroadcast(), processTelemetry(),
                                         detectAndLogChanges(), startPlatformSubscription(),
                                         telemetry constants (TELEMETRY_KEYS, RELAY_KEYS, etc.)
- server/services/scene-engine.js     — executeScene(), checkEventScenes(),
                                         startTimeScheduler(), normalizeSensorVal()
- server/services/index.js            — initServices() wires all deps in correct order,
                                         handles circular dep (control ↔ scene-engine)
                                         via late-binding setSceneEngine()

Key design decisions:
- All services use init() pattern for dependency injection (db, adapterPool)
- control.service uses adapter.sendTelemetry/sendAttributes (not TB directly)
- room.service uses adapter.listDevices/getAllDeviceStates/getDeviceAttributes
- Command verification uses adapter.getCapabilities().commandVerify guard
- WebSocket require('ws') is lazy-loaded to keep module loading clean

Next: PR3 will extract route handlers and shrink index.js to ~150 lines.
