- AdapterPool reads iot_ first, falls back to tb_
- Hotel create/update writes BOTH old and new columns

SERVER CHANGES:
- platform.js: discover route reads iot_ with tb_ fallback
- platform.js: hotel list/detail exposes both tbConfigured and iotConfigured
- platform.js: hotel create/update writes both column sets

CLIENT CHANGES:
- PlatformDashboard.jsx: 'ThingsBoard' → 'IoT Platform' in all labels
